From: audiocore contributors
Subject: [PATCH] increase GGML_MAX_NAME from 64 to 128

Some Qwen3-TTS and MOSS-TTS tensor names exceed 64 characters, which
silently truncates names in ggml's debug/log paths and breaks tensor
lookups done by name. Bump the cap to 128.

Upstream-Status: Pending
---
 ggml/include/ggml.h | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/ggml/include/ggml.h b/ggml/include/ggml.h
--- a/ggml/include/ggml.h
+++ b/ggml/include/ggml.h
@@ -226,7 +226,7 @@
 #define GGML_MAX_OP_PARAMS      64
 
 #ifndef GGML_MAX_NAME
-#   define GGML_MAX_NAME        64
+#   define GGML_MAX_NAME        128
 #endif
 
 #define GGML_DEFAULT_N_THREADS  4

